    "max_size": 5000000
   }
  },
  "permissions": {
   "*@08chan": true,[/code]

I wish I were a pro at javascript, but I am not.  To me this seems to say "don't ignore any files and specifically accept content from these 08chan files while not allowing new 08chan certs."
